t."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p36","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"4.2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_4","part":"s1p36","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Party B warrants that, during the lease term, it will not alter the purposes agreed in the preceding paragraph without the written consent of Party A and before being subject to the examination and approval of competent department."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p37","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p37","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Delivery Date and Lease Term"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p38","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5.1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_25","part":"s1p38","offsets":[{"start":74,"text":"March 1, 2015"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_26","part":"s1p38","offsets":[{"start":126,"text":"June 30, 2015"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p39","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5.2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p39","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Upon expiry of the lease term, Party A has the right to repossess the Premises, while Party B shall return the same as scheduled."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"reinstatement_clause","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_12","part":"s1p39","offsets":[{"start":134,"text":"In case Party B needs to continue to lease the Premises, it shall file a written application for renewal to Party A three months in advance of the expiry of the lease term, while Party A will reply to Party B indicating whether it agrees to such renewal within one month from the date when Party B’s written application is received."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p40","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p40","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Rent, Method and Term of Payment"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p41","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6.1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p41","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Both parties agree that, the unit rent per square meter of construction area of the Premises per day is RMB Four Point Two Zero (RMB4.20), and total amount is RMB Six Hundred and Seventeen Thousand Three Hundred and Ninety Eight Point Forty Five(RMB617,398.45)"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p42","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6.2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p42","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"The rent of the Premises shall be paid before use. The rent shall be paid to Party A in two installments, of which RMB One Hundred and Fifty Six Thousand Eight Hundred and Seventy Nine Point Ninety Three (RMB 156,879.93) shall be paid to Party A prior to March 1 of the current year, and RMB Four Hundred and Sixty Thousand Five Hundred and Eighteen Point Fifty Two (RMB 460,518.52) shall be paid to Party A prior to April 1. Where the final payment date of each installment coincides with a Saturday, Sunday or a public holiday, then the final payment date shall be postponed to the first working day subsequent to the holiday. In case Party B defaults on payment, it must pay an overdue fine equivalent to 0.05% of the due and unpaid rent for each delayed day."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p43","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p43","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Lease Deposit and Other Expenses"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p44","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7.1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p44","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Both parties agree that, within three days as from the date of signing hereof, Party B shall pay Party A lease deposit, which is equivalent to three-month rent, that is, RMB Four Hundred and Sixty One Thousand Seven Hundred and Eighty Three Point Sixty Seven (RMB 461,783.67). Upon collection of lease deposit, Party A shall issue a receipt to Party B."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"guarantee_transferable","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p45","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"During the lease term, Party B may not set off the lease deposit against the rent of the Premises."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"guarantee_transferable","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p45","offsets":[{"start":99,"text":"When this Contract is terminated upon expiry of the lease term, within 10 working days after Party B pays off relevant expenses and goes through the return and handover procedures of the Premises with the Premises management department, the lease deposit paid by Party B will be refunded by Party A interest-free; in case Party B fails to pay off relevant expenses and causes any economic loss to Party A due to any cause attributable to Party B, Party A has the right to deduct relevant amount from the deposit and return the remaining portion to Party B interest-free. Where the lease deposit is insufficient for deduction, Party B shall otherwise pay the insufficient portion."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"reinstatement_clause","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p46","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7.2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p46","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"During the lease term, all water, electricity, communications, equipment and other expenses incurred in connection with the use of the Premises shall be borne by Party B."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"services_charges","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p47","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7.3"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p48","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7.4"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p49","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p49","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Use Requirements and Maintenance Responsibilities for the Premises"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p50","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8.1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p51","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8.2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p52","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8.3"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p53","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8.4"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p54","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8.5"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p54","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"When this Contract is cancelled or terminated, if there are structures added or improved by Party B subject to the written consent of Party A, Party B shall be responsible for restoring the Premises to its original state, except any reasonable wear and tear. Until the Premises is inspected and accepted by Party A, Party B may not handle check-out procedures."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"reinstatement_clause","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p55","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"9."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p55","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Return of the Premises"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p56","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"9.1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p56","offsets":[{"start":96,"text":"Party B shall return the Premises upon expiry of the lease term of this Contract or termination of this Contract for any reason. Where Party B delays returning the Premises without the consent of Party A, Party B shall pay Party A the use fees payable during the occupation of the Premises equivalent to two times of the daily rent for each delayed day. Party B agrees that, if it delays in restoring the Premises to its original state and returning the same for 15 days, Party A shall have the right to enter the Premises at its option, meanwhile, Party B shall be deemed to waive the ownership and right of use in the decoration, facilities, 